About
=====
VPixels is a library for generating images. It supports BMP and GIF format.
VPixels is written in C++. Other the C++ interface, it also provides
programming interfaces for scripting language Lua and Python. You can write
programs in C++, Lua or Python to create images and to manipulate pixels of
images.

