Build and Install
=================
Please see instructions in file INSTALL.

Directories
===========
  cmake/    - files for CMake build
  example/  - examples of using VPixels in C++, Lua and Python
  include/  - C++ header files
  src/      - C++ source files
  test/     - tests
 